# Axiomancy spell names + descriptions (file-11 render). Auto-generated from the approved sheet.
spell-sapping_sting = Sapping Sting
spell-sapping_sting-desc = You bleed a sliver of a creature's vitality away with a touch of premature age — minor necrotic damage, and the sapped target stumbles to the ground.
spell-magnify_gravity = Magnify Gravity
spell-magnify_gravity-desc = Gravity briefly multiplies in a small zone. Creatures caught take force damage and are pressed down — their speed halved until the weight lifts.
spell-gift_of_alacrity = Gift of Alacrity
spell-gift_of_alacrity-desc = You quicken a willing creature's read on the moment, so that when violence breaks they move a half-beat sooner than the rest of the world.
spell-fortunes_favor = Fortune's Favor
spell-fortunes_favor-desc = You seed a thread of luck into yourself or an ally. Once, at a chosen moment, fate bends their way — a roll rerolled, a blow that should have landed turned aside.
spell-immovable_object = Immovable Object
spell-immovable_object-desc = You fix a held object in place against the world's own pull — it will not move, fall, or be shifted by any force short of overwhelming might, becoming an anchor, a barricade, or a step on empty air.
spell-wristpocket = Wristpocket
spell-wristpocket-desc = With a flick of the wrist you fold a small held object into a pocket just out of the world's reach, to be summoned back to hand or sent away again at will.
spell-pulse_wave = Pulse Wave
spell-pulse_wave-desc = You loose a cone of compressed pressure and choose whether it pulls or pushes. Creatures in the cone take force damage and are dragged toward you or flung away.
spell-gravity_sinkhole = Gravity Sinkhole
spell-gravity_sinkhole-desc = A point of crushing force blooms within range and yanks everything toward its centre, dealing force damage and hurling caught creatures inward.
spell-temporal_shunt = Temporal Shunt
spell-temporal_shunt-desc = As a foe strikes or casts, you shove them a step out of time — they vanish for a heartbeat, their attack or spell undone, and reappear staggered where they stood.
spell-gravity_fissure = Gravity Fissure
spell-gravity_fissure-desc = A ravine of gravitational force tears open in a line before you. Creatures along it take force damage and are dragged toward the rift; those nearest are pulled hardest.
spell-tether_essence = Tether Essence
spell-tether_essence-desc = You bind the fates of two creatures into one shared weight: whatever wounds, heals, or afflicts one is mirrored onto the other for as long as the tether holds.
spell-dark_star = Dark Star
spell-dark_star-desc = You collapse a sphere of crushing, lightless gravity centred within range. Within it, sight and sound die and a relentless force grinds at everything caught inside, dealing force damage each round; nothing teleports in or out.
spell-reality_break = Reality Break
spell-reality_break-desc = You shatter the seams between what is and what might have been, plunging one creature into turmoil. Each round it is wracked by one of several collapsing realities chosen at random — blinded by a vanished world, hurled prone by a shifting one, flung through space, or lashed by psychic, force, or biting cold from a might-have-been.
spell-ravenous_void = Ravenous Void
spell-ravenous_void-desc = You open a singularity of destroying gravity. For its duration it drags in everything around it, restrains the caught, and grinds them with massive force damage; matter that fails utterly is crushed out of being.
spell-time_ravage = Time Ravage
spell-time_ravage-desc = You pour years into a single creature in an instant, withering it with brutal, rapid aging — massive necrotic damage, and the survivor is left frail and slowed.
